\": 3508, \"to\": 3513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sneesby was adamant the strike would not affect the coverage and Nine would continue to \\\"seamlessly deliver the best coverage for our audiences\\\".\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sneesby\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3544}, {\"ngram\": \"the strike\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3567}, {\"ngram\": \"the coverage\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"Nine\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"the best coverage\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"our audiences\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More details emerged this week on where the cuts would fall: 10 to 15 staff on the Age and the Sydney Morning Herald would go; six to eight from the national team of federal politics, business, world and environmental journalists.\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More details\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"the cuts\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \": 10 to 15 staff\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3759}, {\"ngram\": \"the Age\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3770}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sydney Morning Herald\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"federal politics, business, world and environmental journalists\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Would love to be covering my first Olympics.But 70-90 redundancies from a profitable section of the business, no hint of exec bonuses being given up, laughably stingy EBA talks and Scott Cam being put up in a five-star Paris hotel?We have got a few things to sort out first.https://t.co/pgvrobBErH When staff argued for a higher pay offer, Maguire reportedly said if the company went any higher they would have to cut even more staff.\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 4351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4083, \"end\": 4086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org