hing\", \"from\": 4576, \"to\": 4603}, {\"ngram\": \"the ageing mogul\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4620}, {\"ngram\": \"his heir\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4633}, {\"ngram\": \"his other children\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story was taken so seriously by the Sky News Australia host Andrew Bolt thathe threatened to quitif James Murdoch takes over News Corp. How would we cope?pic.twitter.com/AFGLDcN1dE \\\"James could sack me if he did take over, but he would not need to.\", \"from\": 4699, \"to\": 4953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4739, \"end\": 4757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky News Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 4763, \"end\": 4774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Bolt\"}, {\"begin\": 4803, \"end\": 4816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Murdoch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0453274513177143e-56, \"text\": \"James Murdoch\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Murdoch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Murdoch\"}, {\"begin\": 4887, \"end\": 4892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9999501490031031, \"rank\": 4.984933091262158e-05, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The story\", \"from\": 4699, \"to\": 4708}, {\"ngram\": \"thathe\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not be the only one who would not work for him,\\\" Bolt said.\", \"from\": 4954, \"to\": 5021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bolt\", \"from\": 5011, \"to\": 5015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a values thing.\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a values thing\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A freedom thing.\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A freedom thing\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know if he gets that.\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up toMorning Mail Our Australian morning briefing breaks down the key stories of the day, telling you what's happening and why it matters after newsletter promotion \\\"I have not been asked to say this.\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"briefing\", \"from\": 5140, \"to\": 5148}, {\"ngram\": \"the key stories\", \"from\": 5161, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5187}, {\"ngram\": \"newsletter promotion\", \"from\": 5243, \"to\": 5263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not even talked to Lachlan for a couple of years.\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lachlan\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5336}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 5341, \"to\": 5349}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not ask for permission to say this.\\\"\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 5378, \"to\": 5388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the absence ofRupert Murdoch, the chosen son Lachlan hosted the gala dinner at the Australian Museum on Thursday night.\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5428, \"end\": 5435