ts, is so important,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5971, \"to\": 6065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"journalism\", \"from\": 5988, \"to\": 5998}, {\"ngram\": \"real journalism\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6015}, {\"ngram\": \"real journalists\", \"from\": 6021, \"to\": 6037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Journalists first and foremost report the news, accurately and without bias.\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Journalists\", \"from\": 6068, \"to\": 6079}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6114}, {\"ngram\": \"bias\", \"from\": 6139, \"to\": 6143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We report the facts.\", \"from\": 6145, \"to\": 6165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the facts\", \"from\": 6155, \"to\": 6164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We ask questions.\", \"from\": 6166, \"to\": 6183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 6173, \"to\": 6182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We seek the truth.\\\"\", \"from\": 6184, \"to\": 6203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Albanesereportedly saidRupert Murdoch \\\"willed into being a newspaper\\\" in an \\\"act of audacity, of \\u00adambition and of optimism that \\u00adreflects the qualities and the story of our great nation\\\".\", \"from\": 6205, \"to\": 6392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6235, \"end\": 6242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rupert_Murdoch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.633810714763508e-41, \"text\": \"Murdoch\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rupert_Murdoch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rupert_Murdoch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a newspaper\", \"from\": 6262, \"to\": 6273}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"act\", \"from\": 6278, \"to\": 6285}, {\"ngram\": \"audacity\", \"from\": 6289, \"to\": 6297}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00adambition\", \"from\": 6302, 